{"kind":"article","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/swiftsphincs\/signverify"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SwiftSPHINCS\/documentation\/SwiftSPHINCS"]]},"seeAlsoSections":[{"generated":true,"title":"Additional Information","anchor":"Additional-Information","identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiftSPHINCS\/documentation\/SwiftSPHINCS\/KeyManagement","doc:\/\/SwiftSPHINCS\/documentation\/SwiftSPHINCS\/OIDs","doc:\/\/SwiftSPHINCS\/documentation\/SwiftSPHINCS\/Performance","doc:\/\/SwiftSPHINCS\/documentation\/SwiftSPHINCS\/References"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"","text":"","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Messages are signed by secret keys and signatures are verified by public keys."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Signatures can be deterministic or randomized and optionally a hash of the message can be signed"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"instead of the message itself."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Example","text":"Example","level":3,"type":"heading"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["import SwiftSPHINCS","","\/\/ Create the SPHINCS keys","","let (secretKey, publicKey) = SPHINCS.GenerateKeyPair(kind: .SHA2_128f)","","\/\/ Deterministic signature","let deterministicSig = secretKey.Sign(message: [1, 2, 3], randomize: false)","print(\"Deterministic:\", publicKey.Verify(message: [1, 2, 3], signature: deterministicSig))","","\/\/ Randomized signature","let randomizedSig = secretKey.Sign(message: [1, 2, 3], randomize: true)","print(\"Randomized:\", publicKey.Verify(message: [1, 2, 3], signature: randomizedSig))","","\/\/ Pre-hashed signature","let preHashedSig = secretKey.SignPrehash(message: [1, 2, 3], ph: .SHA256)","print(\"Pre-hashed:\", publicKey.VerifyPrehash(message: [1, 2, 3], signature: preHashedSig, ph: .SHA256))"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"giving:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":null,"code":["Deterministic: true","Randomized: true","Pre-hashed: true"],"type":"codeListing"}]}],"sections":[],"metadata":{"role":"article","modules":[{"name":"SwiftSPHINCS"}],"title":"Sign and Verify","roleHeading":"Article"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/SwiftSPHINCS\/documentation\/SwiftSPHINCS\/SignVerify","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"references":{"doc://SwiftSPHINCS/documentation/SwiftSPHINCS/OIDs":{"url":"\/documentation\/swiftsphincs\/oids","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftSPHINCS\/documentation\/SwiftSPHINCS\/OIDs","title":"ASN1 OIDs","kind":"article","role":"article","abstract":[],"type":"topic"},"doc://SwiftSPHINCS/documentation/SwiftSPHINCS/KeyManagement":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftSPHINCS\/documentation\/SwiftSPHINCS\/KeyManagement","kind":"article","url":"\/documentation\/swiftsphincs\/keymanagement","abstract":[],"role":"article","title":"Key Management","type":"topic"},"doc://SwiftSPHINCS/documentation/SwiftSPHINCS/References":{"type":"topic","role":"article","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftSPHINCS\/documentation\/SwiftSPHINCS\/References","url":"\/documentation\/swiftsphincs\/references","abstract":[],"title":"References","kind":"article"},"doc://SwiftSPHINCS/documentation/SwiftSPHINCS":{"abstract":[{"text":"Stateless Hash-Based Digital Signature Standard","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/swiftsphincs","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","title":"SwiftSPHINCS","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftSPHINCS\/documentation\/SwiftSPHINCS"},"doc://SwiftSPHINCS/documentation/SwiftSPHINCS/Performance":{"abstract":[],"title":"Performance","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftSPHINCS\/documentation\/SwiftSPHINCS\/Performance","url":"\/documentation\/swiftsphincs\/performance","type":"topic","kind":"article","role":"article"}}}